</tr>
</table>

<!-- =========================================================================================================================== -->
<h3>border = <var>origin</var></h3>
<!-- =========================================================================================================================== -->

<p>Specify the origin of the leftmost bottom square (eg. <code>a1</code>, <code>e5</code>, ...), and also show coordinates
around the chessboard. In case where the position only shows a section of the complete chessboard, borders and coordinates
for a given board side are shown only if outer squares for that side are visible as well.</p>

<table class="table1">
<tr>
